    "title": "Kuja kwa Bwana kama Hakimu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kuja kwa bwana kama hakimu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Biblia inatuambia kutakuwa na siku ya hukumu. Kitabu cha Yakobo kinawapa wafuasi wa Yesu onyo na ahadi kuhusu siku hiyo. Yakobo anatangaza kuja kwa Bwana siku za usoni kama Hakimu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7-Jas5:9\">5:7–9</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:21\">Isaya 26:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:3\">Mika 1:3</a>). Mungu, ambaye alitoa sheria, ndiye &quot;Hakimu, Yeye anayeweza kuokoa na kuangamiza&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:12\">Yakobo 4:12</a>). Wale wanaompinga Yesu Kristo na kuwatesa wafuasi wake watapata matokeo makali (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:6-Jas2:7\">Yakobo 2:6–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:5-Jas5:6\">5:5–6</a>).</p><p>Mungu atawahukumu wafuasi wa Yesu ikiwa watafanya mambo haya mabaya:</p><ul><li><p>ikiwa hawataweza kuonyesha huruma (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:13\">2:13</a>);</p></li><li><p>ikiwa wanakuwa marafiki wa dunia na maadili yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:4\">4:4</a>);</p></li><li><p>ikiwa wanatenda dhambi kwa maneno yao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:11\">4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:9\">5:9</a>); au</p></li><li><p>ikiwa wanaishi kwa kutosheleza tamaa mbaya (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:1\">4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:16\">16</a>).</p></li></ul><p>Mungu atawahukumu kulingana na sheria iliyokusudiwa kuwaweka huru (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:12\">2:12</a>).</p><p>Kuja kwa Bwana siku zijazo kunaathiri maisha yetu sasa. Mungu tayari anawaheshimu maskini waaminifu na kuwaaibisha matajiri wanaowatendea vibaya (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:9-Jas1:10\">Yakobo 1:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:2-Jas5:3\">5:2–3</a>). Wafuasi wa Yesu tayari ni watu maalum wa Mungu wakati Mungu anarejesha mambo yote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:18\">1:18</a>). Yakobo anasema tunapaswa kutii &quot;sheria ya kifalme&quot; ya ufalme wa Yesu Masihi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:8\">2:8</a>). Wafuasi wa Yesu siku moja watarithi ufalme huu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">2:5</a>).</p><p>Kurudi kwa Yesu huenda hakutafanyika hivi karibuni. Kwa hivyo, Yakobo anawahimiza Wakristo kuwa na uvumilivu na kusubiri kwa subira kurudi kwa Yesu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:3-Jas1:4\">Yakobo 1:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7-Jas5:8\">5:7–8</a>). Watapokea &quot;taji ya uzima&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">1:12</a>) na watapata thawabu za Uadilifu, ambazo zinatokana na maisha ya uaminifu kwa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:18\">3:18</a>).</p><p>Kutokana na hukumu inayokuja, Yakobo anawaagiza wafuasi wa Yesu &quot;kumpinga ibilisi&quot; na &quot;kujisalimisha&quot; kwa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7\">Yakobo 4:7</a>). Tunapaswa &quot;kuomboleza&quot; dhambi zetu na kuishi kwa nia na matendo safi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8-Jas4:9\">4:8–9</a>). Tunapaswa kumsaidia ndugu au dada Mkristo yeyote anayepotoka &quot;kutoka kwenye ukweli&quot; kuelekea kifo cha milele (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:19-Jas5:20\">5:19–20</a>). Kama nabii Eliya, tunapaswa kuwa na imani, na kufanya maombi na ungamo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:13-Jas5:18\">5:13–18</a>). Kama Ayubu, tunapaswa kuvumilia mateso. Hatimaye, tutaelewa ukubwa wa wema na rehema za Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:10\">4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:11\">5:11</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:10\">1 Samweli 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:7-Ps2:12\">Zaburi 2:7–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:11-Ps96:13\">96:11–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:21\">Isaya 26:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:3\">Mika 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">Mathayo 16:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:35-Luke12:48\">Luka 12:35–48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:8\">18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:22-John5:30\">Yohana 5:22–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:42\">Matendo 10:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:5\">1 Wakorintho 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7-Jas5:9\">Yakobo 5:7–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:28\">1 Yohana 2:28</a></p>",
